headline: 2 High-Yield Dividend Stocks to Buy Now
summary: Investing in top consumer brands when they offer high dividend yields can be a rewarding investment strategy.  Dollar General (NYSE: DG) and The Hershey Company (NYSE: HSY) are both offering high dividend yields after their stocks fell over the last year on weak financial results amid sluggish consumer spending.  Here's why investors can count on these companies to navigate near-term headwinds and continue paying generous dividends for years to come.
